{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-92-square-digit-chains","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 92: Lanac brojeva za mraba","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Niz brojeva nastaje tako što se neprekidno sabiraju kvadrati cifara broja kako bi se dobio novi broj, sve dok se ne pojavi broj koji je već viđen.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano,</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 44 → 32 → 13 → 10 → \\boldsymbol{1} → \\boldsymbol{1}\\\\\n&#x26; 85 → \\boldsymbol{89} → 145 → 42 → 20 → 4 → 16 → 37 → 58 → \\boldsymbol{89}\\\\\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Zbog toga će svaki niz koji dostigne 1 ili 89 upasti u beskonačnu petlju. Još zanimljivije je to što će SVAKI početni broj na kraju stići do 1 ili 89.</p>\n<p>Koliko brojeva, počevši od ispod <code>limit</code>, stiže do 89?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3c81000cf542c50fedb","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302209,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-92-square-digit-chains"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function squareDigitChains(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsquareDigitChains(100);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>squareDigitChains(100)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof squareDigitChains(100) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>squareDigitChains(100)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>80</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(squareDigitChains(100), 80);"},{"text":"<p><code>squareDigitChains(1000)</code> treba da vrati <code>857</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(squareDigitChains(1000), 857);"},{"text":"<p><code>squareDigitChains(100000)</code> treba da vrati <code>85623</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(squareDigitChains(100000), 85623);"},{"text":"<p><code>squareDigitChains(10000000)</code> treba da vrati <code>8581146</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(squareDigitChains(10000000), 8581146);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-92-square-digit-chains","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-93-arithmetic-expressions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-91-right-triangles-with-integer-coordinates","id":"5900f3c81000cf542c50fedb","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-92-square-digit-chains"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}